    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayra-gutierrez-lopez/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-copyright">
    With <i class="fas fa-heart"></i> by Mayra
